otential future on streaming, where the sport could find a much larger pote=
ntial audience than it has now on cable. The popularity of MLB=E2=80=99s in=
ternational players, in particular, could be a draw for global streaming co=
mpanies like Netflix, which has plenty of room to grow in Asia. Japanese vi=
ewership for last year=E2=80=99s World Series, won by <strong>Shohei Ohtani=
